I"~<p>This is a list of some of the works that were frequently consulted when researching the work and life of <a href="/authors/gerhardt">Paul Gerhardt</a>. Books of musical settings and audio are also cited.</p>

<h3 id="text-sources">Text Sources</h3>

<p><a href="/authors/crüger">Crüger, Johann</a>. <em>Geistliche Kirchenmelodien</em>, 1649.<br />
Crüger, Johann. <em>Praxis Pietatis Melica</em>, 1648 and later.<br />
<a href="/authors/ebeling">Ebeling, Johann</a>. <em>Pauli Gerhardi Geistliche Andachten</em>. Berlin, 1666–1667.<br />
<a href="/authors/feustking">Feustking, Johann</a>. <em>Gerhardts Geistreiche Haus- und Kirchenlieder</em>. Zerbst, 1707.<br />
<a href="authors/kelly">Kelly, John</a>. <em>Paul Gerhardt’s Spiritual Songs</em>. London, 1867.<br />
<a href="/authors/massie_r">Massie, Richard</a>. <em>Lyra Domestica</em>. London, 1860, 1864.<br />
<a href="/authors/winkworth">Winkworth, Catherine</a>. <em>Lyra Germanica</em>, First Series, 1855. Second Series, 1858.<br />
Winkworth, Catherine. <em>Chorale Book for England</em>, 1863.<br />
Winkworth, Catherine. <em>Christian Singers of Germany</em>. Macmillan, 1869.</p>

<h4 id="life-and-work"><strong>Life and Work</strong></h4>

<p>Christian Bunners. <em>Paul Gerhardt: Weg, Werk, Wirkung</em> (Göttingen 2006).</p>

<p>Eberhard von Cranach-Sichart. <em>Wach auf, mein Herz, und singe: vollständige Ausgabe seiner Lieder und Gedichte</em>, 5th ed. (Haan 2007).</p>

<p><a href="/authors/hewitt">Hewitt, Theodore Brown</a>. <em>Paul Gerhardt as a Hymn Writer and His Influence on English Hymnody</em>. New Haven: Yale University Press, 1918.</p>

<h4 id="musical-settings"><strong>Musical Settings</strong></h4>

<p>Christian Finke. <em>Sollt ich meinem Gott nicht singen</em> (München 2006).</p>

<h4 id="audio"><strong>Audio</strong></h4>

<p>Bach-Chor Siegen. <em>Die schönsten Choräle von Paul Gerhardt</em> (Gerth Medien 2007).</p>

<p>Gerhard Schnitter. <em>Befiehl du deine Wege. Die schönsten Choräle von Paul Gerhardt</em> (Hänssler Verlag 2000).</p>

<p>Helmuth Rilling. <em>The Complete Works of Bach: Bachakademie Hänssler Edition</em> (Hänssler Verlag 2001).</p>
